{
  "description": "全77カットの表情変化指示書",
  "note": "各カットで表示するキャラクターと表情を指定",
  
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": 1,
      "title": "イントロ",
      "cuts": [
        {"cutId": "s01_01", "characters": []},
        {"cutId": "s01_02", "characters": []},
        {"cutId": "s01_03", "characters": []}
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": 2,
      "title": "退院前カンファ",
      "cuts": [
        {
          "cutId": "s02_01",
          "speaker": "doctor",
          "text": "聖隷さん、入院中の治療で心不全の症状は改善しました。ただ、肺の状態は以前より悪化しています。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_02_worried"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_07_serious"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s02_02",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "type": "thought",
          "text": "（心の声）やっぱり悪くなっているのか...でも家に帰りたい。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_04_thinking"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s02_03",
          "speaker": "doctor",
          "text": "夜間のNPPV（非侵襲的陽圧換気療法）を自宅でも続けることをお勧めしますが、いかがですか？",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_02_worried"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_04_thinking"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s02_04",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "先生、あの機械は眠れないし、つけるのも大変で...酸素だけでなんとかなりませんか？",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_02_worried"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s02_05",
          "speaker": "doctor",
          "text": "ご本人の意思を尊重します。ただ、急性増悪のリスクは高いことをご理解ください。何かあったらすぐに連絡してください。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_07_serious"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s02_06",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "わかりました。悪くなるなら、それも寿命かなと思っています。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_07_serious"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_02_worried"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": 3,
      "title": "退院・帰宅",
      "cuts": [
        {
          "cutId": "s03_01",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "やっと家に帰ってこられた。やっぱり自分の家が一番落ち着くな。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_06_relieved"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s03_02",
          "speaker": "ichiko",
          "text": "お父さん、おかえりなさい。無理しないでね。ベッドの準備はしてあるから。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_01_smile"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s03_03",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "ありがとう。入院中は夜も眠れなかったから、今日はゆっくり休めそうだ。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_09_grateful"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s03_04",
          "speaker": "ichiko",
          "text": "酸素の機械も業者さんが設置してくれたわ。使い方は覚えてる？",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_04_thinking"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s03_05",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "ああ、3年も使っているから大丈夫だよ。安静時は2リットル、動くときは4リットルに上げればいいんだろう？",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_01_smile"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s03_06",
          "speaker": "ichiko",
          "text": "明日から訪問看護師さんが来てくれるって。週2回、火曜と木曜に来てくれるそうよ。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_01_smile"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": 4,
      "title": "訪問看護（初回）",
      "cuts": [
        {
          "cutId": "s04_01",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "聖隷さん、はじめまして。訪問看護ステーションの山田です。今日からよろしくお願いします。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s04_02",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "よろしくお願いします。こうして家に来てもらえると助かります。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_09_grateful"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s04_03",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "まず、お体の状態を確認させてくださいね。血圧と脈拍、酸素飽和度を測りますね。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s04_04",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "血圧120/75、脈拍78回、SpO2は96%ですね。酸素2リットルで安定しています。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_medical_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s04_05",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "胸の音を聴かせてください...少しヒューヒューという音がしますね。痰は出ますか？",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_medical_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_04_thinking"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s04_06",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "ええ、白っぽい痰が出ることはありますが、自分で出せています。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s04_07",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "それは良かったです。痰の色が黄色や緑色に変わったり、熱が出たりしたら、すぐに連絡してくださいね。感染の兆候かもしれませんから。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_07_serious"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": 5,
      "title": "入浴介助",
      "cuts": [
        {
          "cutId": "s05_01",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "聖隷さん、今日はお風呂に入りましょうか。奥様が準備してくださっていますね。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s05_02",
          "speaker": "ichiko",
          "text": "タオルと着替えは用意してあります。お風呂の温度は39度にしてあるわ。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s05_03",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "ありがとうございます。聖隷さん、入浴前に酸素を4リットルに上げておきましょうね。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s05_04",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "入浴は体力使うからね。苦しくならないか少し心配だな。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_02_worried"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s05_05",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "ゆっくり入りましょう。洗髪や体を洗うのは私がお手伝いしますね。腕を上げる動作は息を吐きながら行いましょう。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s05_06",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "久しぶりのお風呂だ。やっぱり気持ちいいな。一人だとなかなか入れないから、助かるなあ。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_06_relieved"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s05_07",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "お湯に浸かるのは5分程度にしておきましょう。長湯は心臓に負担がかかりますからね。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": 6,
      "title": "呼吸リハビリ",
      "cuts": [
        {
          "cutId": "s06_01",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "聖隷さん、今日は呼吸リハビリをしましょう。体力を維持するためにとても大切なんですよ。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s06_02",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "リハビリか...正直、苦しくなるのが怖くてあまりやっていないんだ。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_02_worried"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s06_03",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "そうですよね。でも、動かないでいると筋力が落ちて、もっと息切れしやすくなってしまうんです。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_07_serious"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s06_04",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "まず、口すぼめ呼吸を練習しましょう。鼻から吸って、口をすぼめてゆっくり吐きます。吐く時間を吸う時間の2倍くらいにするのがコツです。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s06_05",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "こうですか？フーッ...",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_medical_03_pursed_lip"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s06_06",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "上手です！この呼吸法は、気道が狭くなるのを防いで、息を吐きやすくしてくれます。苦しくなった時にも使えますよ。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_01_smile"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s06_07",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "体力が戻ったら、家族と外食に行きたいと思ってるんだ。温泉旅行も夢だけどね。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_01_smile"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s06_08",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "それは素敵な目標ですね！外食に行けるように、一緒に頑張りましょう。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_01_smile"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_01_smile"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": 7,
      "title": "薬局",
      "cuts": [
        {
          "cutId": "s07_01",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "処方箋を持ってきました。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "pharmacist", "position": "right", "expression": "pharmacist_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s07_02",
          "speaker": "pharmacist",
          "text": "聖隷さん、こんにちは。今回のお薬を確認しますね。吸入薬のスピリーバは、毎日同じ時間に使っていますか？",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "pharmacist", "position": "right", "expression": "pharmacist_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s07_03",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "朝と夜に使っています。忘れたことはないですよ。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_01_smile"},
            {"id": "pharmacist", "position": "right", "expression": "pharmacist_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s07_04",
          "speaker": "pharmacist",
          "text": "素晴らしいですね。吸入後はうがいを忘れずにしてくださいね。口腔カンジダの予防になります。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "pharmacist", "position": "right", "expression": "pharmacist_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s07_05",
          "speaker": "pharmacist",
          "text": "プレドニゾロンは炎症を抑えるお薬ですが、長期使用で骨粗鬆症のリスクがありますので、カルシウムを意識して摂ってくださいね。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "pharmacist", "position": "right", "expression": "pharmacist_07_serious"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s07_06",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "わかりました。牛乳を飲むようにします。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "pharmacist", "position": "right", "expression": "pharmacist_01_smile"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": 8,
      "title": "かかりつけ医受診",
      "cuts": [
        {
          "cutId": "s08_01",
          "speaker": "doctor",
          "text": "聖隷さん、退院後1ヶ月ですね。調子はいかがですか？",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s08_02",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "おかげさまで、大きく悪くなることはなく過ごせています。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_01_smile"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s08_03",
          "speaker": "doctor",
          "text": "訪問看護の記録を見ると、SpO2も安定していますね。体重が少し減っているのが気になりますが...",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_02_worried"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s08_04",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "食欲はあるんですが、あまり量が食べられなくて。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_02_worried"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s08_05",
          "speaker": "doctor",
          "text": "COPDの方は呼吸にエネルギーを使うので、体重が減りやすいんです。少量でも高カロリーなものを摂るようにしてください。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s08_06",
          "speaker": "doctor",
          "text": "感染予防も大切です。人混みは避けて、手洗い・うがいを徹底してくださいね。インフルエンザと肺炎球菌のワクチンは接種していますか？",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_07_serious"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s08_07",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "インフルエンザは毎年打っています。肺炎球菌は5年前に打ちました。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s08_08",
          "speaker": "doctor",
          "text": "では次回、肺炎球菌ワクチンの再接種も検討しましょう。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "doctor", "position": "right", "expression": "doctor_01_smile"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": 9,
      "title": "ケアマネ訪問",
      "cuts": [
        {
          "cutId": "s09_01",
          "speaker": "sato",
          "text": "聖隷さん、奥様、こんにちは。ケアマネジャーの佐藤です。サービスの利用状況を確認させてください。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "sato", "position": "right", "expression": "sato_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s09_02",
          "speaker": "ichiko",
          "text": "訪問看護は週2回来てもらっていて、とても助かっています。お風呂も安心して入れるようになりました。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "left", "expression": "ichiko_01_smile"},
            {"id": "sato", "position": "right", "expression": "sato_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s09_03",
          "speaker": "sato",
          "text": "それは良かったです。聖隷さん、他に困っていることはありますか？",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "sato", "position": "right", "expression": "sato_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s09_04",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "買い物に行けなくなったのが困っているかな。車を運転しなくなったから。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_02_worried"},
            {"id": "sato", "position": "right", "expression": "sato_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s09_05",
          "speaker": "sato",
          "text": "では、訪問介護で買い物支援を追加することもできますよ。また、配食サービスという選択肢もあります。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "sato", "position": "right", "expression": "sato_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s09_06",
          "speaker": "ichiko",
          "text": "娘たちが週末に連れ出してくれているけど、毎回は申し訳なくて...",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "left", "expression": "ichiko_02_worried"},
            {"id": "sato", "position": "right", "expression": "sato_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s09_07",
          "speaker": "sato",
          "text": "介護者の負担軽減も大切です。ご家族だけで抱え込まず、使えるサービスは活用してくださいね。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "left", "expression": "ichiko_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "sato", "position": "right", "expression": "sato_07_serious"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": 10,
      "title": "妻との会話",
      "cuts": [
        {
          "cutId": "s10_01",
          "speaker": "ichiko",
          "text": "お父さん、最近少し元気になってきたみたいで嬉しいわ。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s10_02",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "そうかな。まだまだ入院前のようにはいかないけどね。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_02_worried"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s10_03",
          "speaker": "ichiko",
          "text": "無理しなくていいのよ。苦しそうなのを見ているのが一番辛いから。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_02_worried"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s10_04",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "市子には迷惑をかけているな。家事も全部やってもらって...",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_02_worried"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s10_05",
          "speaker": "ichiko",
          "text": "何言ってるの。50年以上一緒にいるんだから、今さらよ。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s10_06",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "体力が戻ったら、また二人で外食に行きたいな。旅行は難しいかもしれないけど。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_01_smile"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s10_07",
          "speaker": "ichiko",
          "text": "近場でいいじゃない。孫たちも連れて、みんなで美味しいもの食べに行きましょう。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_01_smile"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s10_08",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "そうだな。それを目標に、リハビリも頑張るよ。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_09_grateful"},
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "right", "expression": "ichiko_01_smile"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "sceneId": 11,
      "title": "急変時の対応",
      "cuts": [
        {
          "cutId": "s11_01",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "聖隷さん、今日は急に具合が悪くなった時の対応について確認しておきましょう。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s11_02",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "入院中も説明を受けたけど、改めて教えてください。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s11_03",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "まず、いつもより息苦しさが強くなったら、酸素を4リットルに上げて、口すぼめ呼吸をしながら楽な姿勢をとってください。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_07_serious"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s11_04",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "それでも改善しない場合や、次のような症状があったらすぐに連絡してください。①発熱がある ②痰の色が黄色や緑色に変わった ③胸の痛みがある ④意識がぼんやりする ⑤唇や爪が紫色になる",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_07_serious"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s11_05",
          "speaker": "kazuo",
          "text": "わかりました。緊急連絡先は冷蔵庫に貼ってあります。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "kazuo", "position": "left", "expression": "kazuo_general_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s11_06",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "奥様も、何か気になることがあれば遠慮なく連絡してくださいね。24時間対応していますから。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "left", "expression": "ichiko_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s11_07",
          "speaker": "ichiko",
          "text": "夜中でも大丈夫なんですか？申し訳ない気がして...",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "left", "expression": "ichiko_02_worried"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_05_neutral"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s11_08",
          "speaker": "yamada",
          "text": "遠慮しないでください。早めに連絡していただいた方が、大事に至らずに済むことが多いんですよ。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "left", "expression": "ichiko_05_neutral"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_01_smile"}
          ]
        },
        {
          "cutId": "s11_09",
          "speaker": "ichiko",
          "text": "わかりました。何かあったらすぐに連絡しますね。",
          "characters": [
            {"id": "ichiko", "position": "left", "expression": "ichiko_06_relieved"},
            {"id": "yamada", "position": "right", "expression": "yamada_01_smile"}
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
